<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得我今天身體狀況不太好<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你來找我玩，我卻這個樣子……
真對不起。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過<delay20 />吃了<tag a="115" b="0" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />
給我的<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />以後，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已經比之前好很多了喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay20 />雖然你難得來，<delay20 />
但是我今天病才剛好，<delay20 />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />身體狀況還不是很好呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak />不過多虧有<tag a="115" b="0" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />送<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />來給我，<delay40 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在已經恢復不少了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真對不起，之前你來我家的時候，<delay20 />
我沒什麼精神……<delay40 />
因為之前我得了感冒一直沒好。<pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過多虧有<tag a="115" b="0" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />送<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />來給我，<delay40 />
我現在已經完全康復了喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />前陣子你難得來找我，<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我卻因為身體不舒服，<delay20 />
沒辦法好好招待你，真是對不起。<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過還好在那之後，
有<tag a="115" b="0" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />送<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />來給我，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我現在已經恢復健康了喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得我今天身體狀況不太好，<delay20 />
所以都不敢太勉強自己呢。<delay40 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我該不會感冒了吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過<tag a="115" b="0" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />有送<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />來給我，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想吃完<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />以後，
還是先休息一下好了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大概是因為我最近忙過頭了，
才會不小心感冒吧<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />太勉強自己果然對身體不好呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />剛才我已經先吃過
<tag a="115" b="0" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />送給我的<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天就好好休息一下吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />前陣子<delay20 />我不小心感冒了……<delay40 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我明明平常也滿注重<delay20 />
預防疾病和健康管理的呀？<pageBreak />不過生病那時候，
多虧有<tag a="115" b="0" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />送<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />到我家，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的病才總算好起來<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一個人住的時候，生病真的很痛苦。<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我決定之後要在家裡<delay20 />
多放些<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />以防萬一喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />換季的時候，總是特別容易感冒對吧？<delay40 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我前陣子也曾經突然發燒，<delay20 />
那時候還擔心自己不曉得會怎麼樣呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />幸好<tag a="115" b="0" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />來探病的時候，
還帶了<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />給我，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在我已經完全康復了喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的很謝謝你
剛才送<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />來給我。<pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還好有<tag a="110" b="4" />在，<delay20 />
真是幫了我大忙呢。<delay40 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你非常地可靠喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，
多虧了你給我的<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的身體很快就康復了喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你真是我的救命恩人。<delay40 />
我該怎麼向你道謝才好呢？<delay40 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總之，真的很感謝你，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，
多虧有你送<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />來給我，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看，我已經完全康復了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，
真的很感謝你的幫助！<delay40 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />太謝謝你了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
